data.name: label2.Text
data.value:
Thank you for using the Minecraft Server Client! This will only take a few minutes to complete.
If you have already completed this setup and you are seeing this again, this means that one of the files/folders required to run the server have been deleted, moved, or renamed.
If your server has no problems loading and you continue to see this screen when loading this program, please submit a bug report to this program's GitHub issues page and provide adequate detail about the issue you are facing.
Press Next to continue.
